  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="17752859">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/starlv/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1378208-162.jpg" alt="古戈" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17752859/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17752859/" class="">第8页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/starlv/" class=" " title="古戈">古戈</a>
                (基本月)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="17752859">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">舌头的阶级性非常分明，等而下之的舌头用来打口水战，呼口号，高尚的舌头用来赞美神，最高级的舌头则用来接吻，品味美酒佳肴。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17752859/">(<span class="">5回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-04-11 23:04</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>舌头的阶级性非常分明，等而下之的舌头用来打口水战，呼口号，高尚的舌头用来赞美神，最高级的舌头则用来接吻，品味美酒佳肴。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







